snippet.title: Heli-Cats Scoring Gameplay
snippet.description:
Learn how to get a high score in Heli-Cats with a mission 1 Cat A run. Comparing this to the mission 1 survival gameplay video shows a score more than 3 times of that.

Heli-Cats is a dual elevation horizontal 2D co-op shoot'em up arcade action game on Steam. Switch between a high and low elevation to stay safe from traditionally unavoidable enemy fire. However, you have to put yourself in harm's way in order to do damage.

Try the free demo for Windows or macOS at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2262880?utm_source=yt
